{"prompt": "Generate a website for a e-commerce store. The website should be bold and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Bold Red E-commerce</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e53935; /* Bold Red */\n            --secondary-color: #f06292; /* Lighter, complementary red */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #212121; /* Dark background */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 20px;\n            padding-top: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(33, 33, 33, 0.8), rgba(33, 33, 33, 0.8)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x600/e53935/ffffff?text=Bold+Deals') center center/cover no-repeat;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 5rem 2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 2rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border: 2px solid var(--brand-color);\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            border-color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .products {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .product-card {\n            background-color: #333333;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid transparent;\n        }\n\n        .product-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n            border-color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .product-card img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            border: 1px solid #555;\n        }\n\n        .product-card h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .product-card .price {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            display: block;\n        }\n\n        .product-card .add-to-cart {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .product-card .add-to-cart:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n            background-color: #181818;\n            color: #bbb;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>BOLD RED STORE</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#home\">Home</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#products\">Products</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\" id=\"home\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Unleash Your Bold Side</h2>\n            <p>Discover exclusive deals on our latest collection. Shop with confidence and style.</p>\n            <a href=\"#products\" class=\"cta-button\">Shop Now</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container\" id=\"products\">\n        <h2>Featured Products</h2>\n        <div class=\"products\">\n            <div class=\"product-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e53935/ffffff?text=Product+1\" alt=\"Product 1\">\n                <h3>Stylish Red Sneakers</h3>\n                <span class=\"price\">$99.99</span>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/f06292/ffffff?text=Product+2\" alt=\"Product 2\">\n                <h3>Bold Graphic Tee</h3>\n                <span class=\"price\">$45.00</span>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e53935/ffffff?text=Product+3\" alt=\"Product 3\">\n                <h3>Red Leather Wallet</h3>\n                <span class=\"price\">$65.50</span>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/f06292/ffffff?text=Product+4\" alt=\"Product 4\">\n                <h3>Statement Red Necklace</h3>\n                <span class=\"price\">$75.00</span>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container\" id=\"about\" style=\"margin-top: 3rem;\">\n        <h2>About Us</h2>\n        <p>We are passionate about bringing you high-quality, trendsetting products with a bold aesthetic. Our mission is to empower you to express yourself through fashion. We believe in vibrant style and exceptional value.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container\" id=\"contact\" style=\"margin-top: 3rem;\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <p>Have questions or feedback? Reach out to us!</p>\n        <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@boldredstore.com\" style=\"color: var(--secondary-color);\">info@boldredstore.com</a></p>\n        <p>Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Bold Red Store. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}